<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Oswald, sans-serif; font-size: large;"><img style="margin: 0px 10px 10px 0px; vertical-align: middle;" src="http://www.appliedteltech.com/photoFiles/Home-1.png" alt="" width="20" height="30" />Colorado's Business Service Leader</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Applied Telephone Technology, Inc. was founded by Steve Butler in 1978 to provide consulting, sales, installation, and service of&nbsp;telecommunication products to&nbsp;Colorado&rsquo;s business community. We have since become Colorado&rsquo;s business service leader, with over 1,000 satisfied customers.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">We install, maintain, move and service most makes and models of <span>telecommunication</span>&nbsp;systems,&nbsp;equipment and products.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>
