<p style="text-align: justify;">We are an accredited member of the Denver-Boulder Better Business Bureau with over 30 years in good standing and an authorized and certified NEC Dealer.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><br />Applied Telephone is one of the most respected and sought after interconnect companies in Colorado.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">We lead the way in showing companies how to overhead costs and now many businesses are hiring telecommuter &nbsp;employees to work in their business.</p>
